* Long example
2020-12-04 trade Asset:Trading  400 9984 @ 7260 JPY
  settlement     Asset:Settlement
  expense        Expense:Commission    100 JPY

2020-12-04 assert Asset:Settlement   -2906100 JPY

2020-12-07 trade Asset:Trading2  600 9984 @ 7123 JPY
  settlement     Asset:Settlement
  expense        Expense:Commission    100 JPY

2020-12-07 assert Asset:Settlement   -7180000 JPY

2021-02-09 trade Asset:Trading -200 9984 @ 9808 JPY
  settlement     Asset:Settlement
